paragraph.value: In Table  there are the results on the DIVA-HisDB dataset (see Section III-A). Our method achieves nearly perfect results (99.42%) and outperforms state-of-the-art (97.86%) resulting in a error reduction of 80.7%.  Note that the lower end of the heatmap scale compares favourably with state-ofthe-art (see Table I) meaning that regardless of the choice of parameters, our method produces excellent results.
